Project Title: Work on DESI Operations at the University of Wyoming
additiol information prop:
The DOE Funding Opportunity Announcement (FOA) will ultimately require 5 fillable PDF forms to be uploaded to Grants.gov. 

I am conscious that I may be using a different version of Adobe Acrobat Reader to Research Services. So, I was unsure whether it would be more useful to Research Services to include the 5 fillable PDFs (mostly completed) or just the attachments that will need to be added to those PDFs. I have therefore include BOTH. 

The 5 fillable PDFs are titled Form-A-* Form-B-*, etc. and the attachments are called, e.g., Form-B-Field7-* where "Form" matches the letter I've assigned to the fillable PDF and "Field" refers to the field on that form where the attachment will be attached. 

Hopefully that all makes sense!
foreign collaboration details: The proposal centers on work with the Dark Energy Spectroscopic Instrument (DESI) collaboration. The DESI collaboration is a huge, intertiol effort comprising hundreds of researchers from many different countries. Technical data arising from the DESI experiment is shared with all collaborators. I have tried to list as many countries as I can who are involved in the DESI collaboration, although DESI researchers frequently move to institutions in new countries.
foreign shipment country: [France, Australia, Israel, Spain, Chi, United Kingdom, Poland, Germany, Switzerland, Italy, Korea, South, Brazil, Mexico, Japan, Taiwan, Denmark, Cada, India, Colombia, Netherlands, Norway]
